### Sentinel REST API — manual test harness
### Use with the VS Code REST Client extension or JetBrains HTTP Client.
### Click "Send Request" above any block, or right-click → Run All.

@host = http://localhost:8081
@adminToken = 123
@email = alice@example.com

### ---------------------------------------------------------------
### Health
### ---------------------------------------------------------------

### Healthcheck (no auth)
GET {{host}}/healthz

### Readiness probe (no auth) — shows engineer count + backend status
GET {{host}}/readyz

### Prometheus metrics (no auth)
GET {{host}}/metrics

### ---------------------------------------------------------------
### Engineer CRUD
### ---------------------------------------------------------------

### Create a new engineer
POST {{host}}/admin/engineers
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "name": "Alice Example",
  "github_username": "alice-example",
  "slack_user_id": "U0ABCDEF",
  "manager_slack_id": "U0MGRABC",
  "daily_budget_usd": 25.00,
  "monthly_budget_usd": 500.00,
  "team": "platform"
}

### Create with duplicate email → expect 409
POST {{host}}/admin/engineers
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "name": "Alice Dupe",
  "github_username": "alice-dupe"
}

### Create with invalid email → expect 400
POST {{host}}/admin/engineers
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "not-an-email",
  "name": "Bad",
  "github_username": "bad"
}

### List all active engineers (with live Redis spend joined)
GET {{host}}/admin/engineers
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get one engineer's detail (history, triggers, latest efficiency snapshot)
GET {{host}}/admin/engineers/{{email}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Partial update — change just the daily budget
PUT {{host}}/admin/engineers/{{email}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "daily_budget_usd": 50.00
}

### Partial update — change name + team
PUT {{host}}/admin/engineers/{{email}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice Renamed",
  "team": "infrastructure"
}

### Update unknown engineer → expect 404
PUT {{host}}/admin/engineers/nobody@example.com
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Nobody"
}

### Soft-delete (sets active = FALSE; historical data preserved)
DELETE {{host}}/admin/engineers/{{email}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Delete unknown engineer → expect 404
DELETE {{host}}/admin/engineers/nobody@example.com
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ---------------------------------------------------------------
### Analytics
### ---------------------------------------------------------------

### Leaderboard, 1 day window
GET {{host}}/admin/leaderboard?window=1d
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Leaderboard, 7 day window (default)
GET {{host}}/admin/leaderboard?window=7d
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Leaderboard, 30 day window
GET {{host}}/admin/leaderboard?window=30d
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Leaderboard, 180 day window
GET {{host}}/admin/leaderboard?window=180d
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Invalid window → expect 400
GET {{host}}/admin/leaderboard?window=999d
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Recent usage events (default limit 100)
GET {{host}}/admin/usage/recent
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Recent usage events with custom limit
GET {{host}}/admin/usage/recent?limit=25
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ---------------------------------------------------------------
### Ops triggers
### ---------------------------------------------------------------

### Force the GitHub collector to run now (async; returns 202)
POST {{host}}/admin/refresh-efficiency
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Force an immediate engineer-registry reload from Postgres
POST {{host}}/admin/registry/refresh
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ---------------------------------------------------------------
### Signal analytics
### ---------------------------------------------------------------

### Efficiency rollup — leaderboard table for one window
###   window options: 1d | 7d | 30d | 180d
GET {{host}}/admin/signals/efficiency?window=30d
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Efficiency rollup — 7-day window
GET {{host}}/admin/signals/efficiency?window=7d
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Efficiency rollup — invalid window → expect 400
GET {{host}}/admin/signals/efficiency?window=999d
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Efficiency rollup — one engineer detail
GET {{host}}/admin/signals/efficiency/{{email}}?window=30d
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Efficiency rollup — unknown engineer → expect 404 ("no rollup yet")
GET {{host}}/admin/signals/efficiency/nobody@example.com?window=30d
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Detected signals — recent (default 7d, all types/severities)
GET {{host}}/admin/signals/events
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Detected signals — critical only
GET {{host}}/admin/signals/events?severity=critical
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Detected signals — burst only
GET {{host}}/admin/signals/events?type=burst
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Detected signals — with a since cutoff + custom limit
GET {{host}}/admin/signals/events?since=2026-05-20T00:00:00Z&limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Detected signals — invalid since → expect 400
GET {{host}}/admin/signals/events?since=not-a-timestamp
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Detected signals — scoped to one engineer
GET {{host}}/admin/signals/events/{{email}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Detected signals — engineer + severity filter
GET {{host}}/admin/signals/events/{{email}}?severity=critical&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ---------------------------------------------------------------
### Auth failures
### ---------------------------------------------------------------

### No Authorization header → expect 401
GET {{host}}/admin/engineers

### Wrong bearer token → expect 401
GET {{host}}/admin/engineers
Authorization: Bearer not-the-right-token
